      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，就是那六个控制位。Infra_WorkerNode放在160到191位，Infra_EtcdCluster放在192到255位，作为Data字段的标注。另外，Source Port和Destination Port分别是0-15位和16-31位，这个标准位置不要动。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我梳理一下：0-15是Source Port，16-31是Destination Port，然后96-111位放那六个控制位——URG在106，ACK在107，PSH、RST、SYN、FIN依次排开。160-191是Infra_WorkerNode，192-255是Data字段标注Infra_EtcdCluster。中间还需要Sequence Number、Acknowledgment Number这些标准字段吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number",
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
